data.description: $5,000 IN SELLER CREDIT TO BE USED HOWEVER BUYER CHOOSES WITH AN EXECUTED CONTRACT BY 10-31! This stunning, one owner property offers 5 bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms, an office and a game room. In addition to the primary bedroom, this floor plan offers a guest bedroom and full bath on the main floor. The private office is complete with beautiful french doors and offers lots of natural light. The kitchen boasts SS appliances, granite countertops, an island perfect for entertaining and opens to the family room complete with a stunning, custom built decorative fireplace. Upstairs you have 3 additional bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a game room. The breathtaking backyard will be your very own oasis complete with a heated pool with waterfalls, spa and lush landscaping, a gas fire pit and a covered outdoor kitchen perfect for entertaining all year round! All appliances to remain with the home making this the perfect, move in ready property! Roof replaced in 2021, new carpet in 2023.
